title: China Is At a Crossroads: What Does That Mean For Your Portfolio
description: Reshma Kapadia, associate editor and Mary Romano, assistant managing editor at Barron's discuss the seismic changes underfoot in China's economy and relationship with the U.S., what it means for foreign policy, corporate strategy and portfolios.
